# AI trace use-case examples (no auth)
# In Cursor/VS Code: install "REST Client" extension, then click "Send Request" above each ### block.
# Change baseUrl if your API runs on another port.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1 — Single generation (one trace, finalized with name/output)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/examples/use-case-1-single-generation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Écris un haïku sur TypeScript."
}

### 2 — Grouped calls (several LLM calls, one trace)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/examples/use-case-2-grouped-calls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompts": [
    "Résume en une phrase : TypeScript.",
    "Traduis en anglais.",
    "Donne un titre."
  ]
}

### 3 — Logical units (one trace per workflow)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/examples/use-case-3-logical-units
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowPrompts": [
    "Workflow A : décris le soleil.",
    "Workflow B : décris la lune.",
    "Workflow C : décris les étoiles."
  ]
}

### 4 — Chat with session (sessionId groups traces in Langfuse)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/examples/use-case-4-chat-session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Dis bonjour en une phrase.",
  "sessionId": "conv-demo-123"
}
